2025-11-05TCCanadian Air Transport Security Authority ActAppointment of the Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, on an interim basisAppointment of Neil Parry of Chelsea, Quebec, to be Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eighteen months, or until such time as a new Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first.N/A
act: Canadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
subject: Appointment of the Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, on an interim basis
precis: Appointment of Neil Parry of Chelsea, Quebec, to be Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term of eighteen months, or until such time as a new Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first.
